<h2>7. Demo Flow (Step by Step)</h2>

<h3>Ops View</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Open <strong>/ops</strong> → login as <code>admin / wiom@2026</code></li>
  <li>Home page shows demo dataset (5 partners, ~84 devices in accountability lists)</li>
  <li>Note partner credentials table — copy usernames + PINs to share with partners</li>
  <li>Click <strong>View Dashboard</strong> → see all partners at "Not Started"</li>
</ol>

<h3>Partner View</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Open <strong>/partner</strong> → login as <code>partner_sunita / 2345</code></li>
  <li>Welcome screen shows "18 devices to account for"</li>
  <li>Click <strong>Start Audit →</strong></li>
  <li>Tap <strong>📷 Scan Barcode</strong> (or click "Enter Device ID manually")</li>
  <li>Enter device IDs from the checklist — watch them tick green</li>
  <li>Note ⚠ grey zone tags on expired-ticket devices</li>
  <li>Try entering a device ID from a different partner → see 🚨 Unauthorized toast</li>
  <li>Click <strong>Review &amp; Submit →</strong> then <strong>Submit Audit</strong></li>
</ol>

<h3>Back to Ops</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Return to <strong>/ops/dashboard</strong> — Sunita Networks now shows "Submitted" badge</li>
  <li>Click the row → see device-level breakdown (verified / missing / unexpected)</li>
  <li>Download <strong>Full Reconciliation CSV</strong>, <strong>State Corrections CSV</strong>, <strong>Missing Devices CSV</strong></li>
</ol>

